          "zh": "Meta超智能实验室发布Muse Spark模型"
        },
        "tl_dr": {
          "en": "Meta's Superintelligence Lab (MSL) has unveiled its first public model, Muse Spark, which is also the first frontier model on their new stack.",
          "zh": "Meta超智能实验室（MSL）发布了其首个公开模型Muse Spark，该模型也是其全新技术栈上的首个前沿模型。"
